name: SeedBox
description: SeedBox is a redesigned launchpad solution-oriented to bring the VC opportunities for the retail investors and bring the best user experience through the termination of the pain points that were bestowed by other launchpad platforms. We address the needs of the market participants, by channeling the best expertise and due diligence on the top-notch projects and companies looking to raise the funds for their private or public rounds, not only by providing the launchpad solution itself but rather by supplying them with the right resources and insights to be equipped for the launch, acting as an incubating platform per se.
